  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "In a bowl, mix Panko breadcrumbs with garlic powder and salt. Add red pepper flakes if desired.",
    "Lightly grease your hands and spread the breadcrumb mixture evenly onto each rice cake.",
    "Place toasted rice cakes on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 5-7 minutes or until golden brown, turning once halfway through cooking time.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool slightly before serving."
